# Introduction

Minimal vignette stub for fast README / figure-layout iteration.
Use `source("vignettes/temp_precompile.R")` from the package root.

```{r fig-logo, echo = FALSE, out.height = "139px", out.width = "120px"}
find_figure("logo.png") |>
  knitr::include_graphics()
```

```{r fig-funders, echo = FALSE, out.height = "58px", out.width = c("155px", "129px", "202px", "219px", "180px", "120px")}
c(
  "svcf_logo.jpeg",
  "czi_logo.png",
  "bioconductor_logo.jpg",
  "vca_logo.png",
  "nectar_logo.png",
  "CSL_Limited_logo.svg.png"
) |>
  find_figure() |>
  knitr::include_graphics()
```

## Sample plot

